类 MySQLStatementBaseVisitor<T>

    直接已知子类:

    public class MySQLStatementBaseVisitor<T>
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.AbstractParseTreeVisitor<T>
implements MySQLStatementVisitor<T>
    This class provides an empty implementation of MySQLStatementVisitor, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
